  "prompt": "What is the best advice you can give to a 17-year-old?",
  "response": "Here are some key pieces of advice for a 17-year-old:\n\n1. Focus on personal growth\n- Develop good habits\n- Learn continuously\n- Be curious and open-minded\n\n2. Education and skills\n- Take your studies seriously\n- Explore your interests\n- Learn practical skills beyond academics\n\n3. Relationships\n- Choose friends wisely\n- Build healthy, supportive relationships\n- Respect yourself and others\n\n4. Financial literacy\n- Start saving money\n- Learn basic financial management\n- Understand the value of money\n\n5. Mental health\n- Prioritize self-care\n- Learn stress management techniques\n- Don't be afraid to seek help if needed\n\n6. Goal setting\n- Set realistic short-term and long-term goals\n- Create plans to achieve them\n- Be adaptable and willing to adjust\n\n7. Personal responsibility\n- Take ownership of your actions\n- Learn from mistakes\n- Don't blame others\n\n8. Explore and take risks\n- Try new experiences\n- Step out of your comfort zone\n- Don't be afraid of failure\n\n9. Build confidence\n- Believe in yourself\n- Develop a positive self-image\n- Practice self-compassion\n\n10. Stay true to your values\n- Know what's important to you\n- Make decisions aligned with your principles\n- Don't compromise your integrity",
